18 visitor visa, as provided under 22 C.F.R., Section 41.31 et. seq,
19 shall not operate a commercial motor vehicle within this state.
20 2. A holder of such a visa, as provided in this subsection,
21 found to be operating a commercial motor vehicle within this state
